<p class="ko" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">출처: 이더파이(ether.fi) 및 넥서스뮤추얼(Nexus Mutual) 공동 발표, 크립토슬레이트(CryptoSlate), 디크립트(Decrypt), 크립토브리핑(CryptoBriefing), 크립토포테이토(CryptoPotato), 코인데스크(CoinDesk, "Ethereum Rare Mass Slashing Event Linked To Operator Issues"), 넥서스뮤추얼 공식 문서(docs.nexusmutual.io).</p>
<p class="en" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Sources: Joint announcement by ether.fi and Nexus Mutual, CryptoSlate, Decrypt, CryptoBriefing, CryptoPotato, CoinDesk ("Ethereum Rare Mass Slashing Event Linked To Operator Issues"), Nexus Mutual official documentation (docs.nexusmutual.io).</p>
